**$x$-intercept:** Set $y = 0$:
\[
 3x = 12 \Rightarrow x = 4
\]
The $x$-intercept is $(4, 0)$.

**$y$-intercept:** Set $x = 0$:
\[
 2y = 12 \Rightarrow y = 6
\]
The $y$-intercept is $(0, 6)$.

